<section xmlns="https://code.dccouncil.us/schemas/dc-library" xmlns:codified="https://code.dccouncil.us/schemas/codified" xmlns:codify="https://code.dccouncil.us/schemas/codify" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude">
  <prefix>§</prefix>
  <num>19-1702.03</num>
  <heading proof="needed">Presumption of unlimited authority.</heading>
  <para>
    <num undesignated="true">(a)</num>
    <text>Subject to <cite path="§19-1702.05">§ 19-1702.05</cite>, and unless the terms of the instrument creating a power of appointment manifest a contrary intent, the power is:</text>
    <para>
      <num>(1)</num>
      <text>Presently exercisable;</text>
    </para>
    <para>
      <num>(2)</num>
      <text>Exclusionary; and</text>
    </para>
    <para>
      <num>(3)</num>
      <text>Except as otherwise provided in <cite path="§19-1702.04">§ 19-1702.04</cite>, general.</text>
    </para>
  </para>
